CustomerPurge is a BusinessTask
    owned by ar

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            Reports
                CustomerPurgeReport
                GroupCustomerPurgeListing

    Parameters
    	FinanceEnterpriseGroup
        Company                 is a ReceivableCompany
        CustGroup               is a CustomerGroup
        DeleteAraudit           is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        ArauditDate             is Date
        SetStatusDel            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        Archive                 is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"

        Customer
        	context of CustGroup
        CudName                 is AlphaUpper size 30
        StartDate               is Date
        MajClass                is a CustomerMajorClass
           	context of FinanceEnterpriseGroup
        MinClass                is a CustomerMinorClass
        	context of FinanceEnterpriseGroup
        CreditAnlyst            is a CreditAnalyst
        Salesman                is a SalesRepresentative

    Parameter Rules
    	FinanceEnterpriseGroup
			initial value is actor.context.FinanceEnterpriseGroup
            
        CustGroup   
            if (Company entered)
                default to Company.CustomerGroupField.CustomerGroup
    	
        DeleteAraudit
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        SetStatusDel
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        Archive
            required

    Actions
        CustomerPurge is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
